[テオ f=10]「Actually...」[k]
The next day, I told Maria and everyone in the party what had happened last night.[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=05
[マリア v=va123 f=05]「Blue is that guy you were talking about before...!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I'm sorry...! It was all my fault...!」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=10
[マリア v=va124 f=10]「That's all on him, not you. It's not your fault...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「No, it was my fault! It was my fault for not protecting Riselle.」[k]
[テオ f=09]「And besides... If I hadn't gotten involved with that guy in the first place, it would never have happened... !」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=09
[マリア v=va125 f=09]「You...」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn it...! What should I do...?」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=57
[マリア v=va126 f=57]「There's no point in feeling sorry for myself now! Instead, let's focus on helping Riselle first and foremost right now!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Maria...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah, that's right.」[k]
Maria is certainly right. Let's focus on rescuing Riselle now.[k]
...That said, it isn't easy to regain a member who has been stolen from you through a duel.[k]
Two hurdles must be overcome if you want to get back a member who was taken from you in a duel.[k]
The first is to wait for a certain [b]captivity period[/b] to pass.[k]
During this period, the other party has unconditional ownership of the co-opted member, and they can't be taken back, no matter what. If a member disobeys this rule, he or she will be erased from existence by the power of the Duel God.[k]
The second is to beat your opponent in a duel again. This is the hardest hurdle of all.[k]
The right to take back Riselle is only restored after the captivity period has expired, but it isn't unconditional. After that, we must defeat Blue and the others in a duel to so so.[k]
[マックス f=11]「Blue finally found us?! Are you kidding me?!」[k]
Max is holding his head in his hands, looking completely terrified now he knows that Blue has found us.[k]
[マックス f=27]「Hey, [テオ]! Let's get out of here right now! They let us off the hook, so now's our only chance!」[k]
[マリア v=va127 f=07]「What are you talking about, Max?! We have to get Riselle back! Are you really planning on abandoning her?!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Even if you say that, there's nothing we can do until the time's up! And afterwards...」[k]
[マックス f=17]「Our opponent would be none other than Blue! And you were no match for him even now, right? There's no way we can win! I feel bad for her, but Riselle will just have to bear it...」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=11
[マリア v=va128 f=11]「Don't say something so stupid! I'll get her back, even if I have to do it alone!」[k]
[マックス f=25]「I understand how you feel, but if you go up against Blue, you'll lose, and this time you'll become Blue's prisoner.」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=10
[マリア v=va129 f=10]「That's...」[k]
Maria stammers. Indeed, given Blue's strength, it wouldn't be unreasonable for her to give up.[k]
Maria, however, looked up again and said with a determined look on her face.[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=11
[マリア v=va130 f=11]「Still, I won't give up! I'll get Riselle back no matter how many months or years it takes! What about you guys!」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Maria, I feel the same way. We'll get Riselle back one day. I'm sure of it!」[k]
[マリア v=va131 f=05]「Oh...!」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=02
[マリア v=va132 f=02]「...Thank you. I knew you'd say that.」[k]
There is no way I would abandon Riselle. I love her. I have to get her back, no matter what.[k]
@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'

[   if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd037 e=通常 f=09]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg028 e=通常 f=10]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh037 e=通常 f=09]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs039 e=通常 f=09]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve038 e=通常 f=10]「Captain...」[k]
[endif]

The party members look at me with concern. I turn to them.[k]
[テオ f=06]「I have to get Riselle back.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...But you all have a right to choose. It's risky, so I'm not going to force you to go along. If you don't want to, you have my blessing to leave the party. 」[k]

[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh038 f=07]「Don't be silly, Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd038 f=07]「Don't be silly, Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg029 f=08]「What are you talking about, Captain...!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve039 f=07]「Don't be ridiculous, Captain!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs040 f=07]「Don't be ridiculous, Captain!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「[キャラ]...!」[k]

[   if exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg030 f=08]「Riselle is part of our party... We can't abandon her...!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve040 f=08]「I'm going with you. I won't abandon her.」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs041 f=07]「I'm going with you! I can't abandon Riselle either!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh039 f=07]「Riselle is our friend! We've got to help her!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd039 f=07]「Riselle is our friend! We've got to help her!」[k]
[endif]

[   if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd040 f=07]「Let's get stronger and stronger and defeat that Blue!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh040 f=07]「Let's get stronger and stronger and defeat that Blue!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs042 f=15]「Let's defeat that Blue guy! I'm sure we can do it someday!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve041 f=15]「Let's defeat this Blue person! I'm sure we can manage it.」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg031 f=08]「Let's beat that Blue... even if it takes some time...」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=01]「Everyone...!」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=14
[マリア v=va133 f=14]「Thank you, guys... I'm so happy you'd do that for Riselle...!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Seriously...? You guys all want to fight Blue...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Then it's settled. We can't do it right now, but we will definitely get Riselle back eventually!」[k]

[if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh041 f=03]「Yeah!」[k][endif]
[if exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve042 f=15]「Certainly!」[k][endif]
[if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd041 f=03]「Let's do our best!」[k][endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg032 f=02]「I'll do my best...!」[k][endif]
[if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs043 f=15]「I'll do it!」[k][endif]

@fgf c=マリア f=03
[マリア v=va134 f=03]「Let's all do our best!」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=02
[マリア v=va135 f=02]「Well, I guess this is where I say goodbye to Max. Later, bye.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「W-w-wait a minute! Everyone!」[k]
[マリア v=va136 f=05]「What? You don't want to fight Blue.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「I don't want to fight... but if everyone says so, I guess I have to go along with you...」[k]
[マリア v=va137 f=05]「If you don't want to, you don't have to force yourself to come along, okay?」[k]
[マックス f=09]「I'll be right behind you! Please let me tag along!」[k]
[マリア v=va138 f=02]「You should have just said so from the beginning.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Thanks, Max. Let's keep fighting together!」[k]
[マックス f=09]「Oh, man... I can't help it. If it comes to this, I'll stick with you until the very end.」[k]
[textoff]
@st
@se f=up3
@notice text="<y>Maria and Max have joined the party!"
@out
@w2

; サファイアシティの酒場
@bg f=0012
@mu f=anxiety
[texton w=0]
I decided to look for Blue first.[k]
The purpose is to find out places he goes, and where he usually stays.[k]
When the time comes to rescue Riselle, if we don't know where he is, we'll be in trouble.[k]
Of course, that might not be easy to find out, but it's better than having no clue.[k]
Also, I wanted to make sure nothing worse happens to Riselle... though it might be pointless to say that.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[マックス f=09]「Oh... I don't want to meet Blue again...」[k]
In the meantime, Max and I go to the bar and wait for Blue and the others to arrive.[k]
They are adventurers, after all. Nothing is possible without receiving quests at the bar. So if we wait here, we'll definitely meet them.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Are they not coming today...? Maybe I should try another day...[k]
[ベトリヌス f=05]「Why are you hanging around in my bar?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah... The bar master...」[k]
After a few hours of waiting for Blue in the seating area, I was approached by Vetrinus, the owner of this tavern.[k]
[テオ f=06]「Well... I'm looking for an adventurer named Blue. I really need to meet with him...」[k]
[ベトリヌス f=06]「Ah, those adventurers went back to the town they came from.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What? Really?」[k]
[ベトリヌス f=02]「Those guys aren't qualified to take requests at this bar, so I'd never give them work. It's a matter of reputation for this bar.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Really? In the previous town, he was so influential...」[k]
[ベトリヌス f=02]「Anyway, I know all about those particular adventurers. There's no way I'd let people like that work here.」[k]
[マックス f=05]「So that's how it is. That makes sense. If they can't work as adventurers here, they'd have no choice but to leave.」[k]
[ベトリヌス f=02]「I value trust above all else. I don't tolerate any dishonest behavior, such as subcontracting or reward skimming. Adventurers who do such things aren't welcome in my bar.」[k]
[ベトリヌス f=00]「My tavern has become the most highly regarded in the country. But that's only due to my strict enforcement of the rules and keeping an eye out for dishonest adventurers.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Then Blue can't do anything here. I guess he went back home so he could make money where the restrictions are looser.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
So Blue must be in his own hideout in Bravetown...[k]
According to the owner, there is a good chance that he will have to remain in Bravetown. If I go there, I might be able to meet Riselle.[k]
[マックス f=01]「At any rate, we can't get Riselle back for a month no matter what we do, so we just have to focus on getting stronger for a while, right?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Well, yes...」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

; 夜・宿屋
@bg f=0001
[texton w=0]
That night. I remembered the fight with Blue in the park.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
...Blue was strong.[k]
I thought I'd become strong enough that I could fight Blue. But in reality, there was still a gap in power.[k]
It was a bad situation, since not all the party were there.  But there were only three opponents even so.[k]
In terms of numbers, it wasn't a huge disadvantage. But even if all the party was there, we probably wouldn't have won.[k]
...Because no one can beat Blue. Even if we band together, we still can't beat him.[k]
To be honest, I was elated after winning the tournament. I had mistakenly thought that I'd become strong enough.[k]
And because of that hubris, I lost my precious Riselle...[k]
[テオ f=09]「...Damn!」[k]
I feel pathetic. Will I ever be able to beat Blue...?[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
...No, I mustn't think such things. I have to defeat Blue. To rescue Riselle.[k]
I will become stronger. Everyone in the party will become stronger and next time, we will beat Blue and his friends.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
However, there is one more issue, if we want to defeat Blue.[k]
That sylph girl Miredy, who was with Blue.[k]
Thanks to the mysterious power she invoked, neither of us could use magic. We had no choice but to face Blue in disadvantageous melee combat.[k]
What was that phenomenon?[k]
Unlike the [emb exp='o.サイレンス.displayName'] spell, it didn't seal the mouth of a mage. It was more like magic could no longer penetrate this area.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

; 翌日・シュバルツの家
@mu f=evil
@fg c=シュバルツ f=00 b
@bgf f=0012
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=02]「That's Anti-Magic.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Anti-Magic?」[k]
Desperate for some help, I turned to Mr. Schwarz for advice.[k]
He told me the name of a technique I'd never heard of.[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I have only met a few people who could use this technique. It's that rare.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「It prohibits magic in all the area around the caster, rendering all magic and magic items ineffective.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Prohibiting all magic in the area...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Of course, doing so also neutralizes the magic of your allies. After all, you can't activate any magic within the space at all.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「However, that's isn't necessarily a problem, depending on your allies. For a physically oriented party, this can be a very effective tactic.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I see...」[k]
Who would have thought such an unfair technique existed? It renders mages completely useless. It's a perfect technique for Blue, who has a superhuman body.[k]
How on earth can we counter such a technique... Is the only way to hit hard enough to beat Blue?[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Don't worry. There are ways to deal with this.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Really?!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「The [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'] spell.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「[emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName']?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Since you're an adventurer, you must know about magical effects.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「We can use magic to improve our defense, increase our speed, levitate our party...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「But [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'] erases all those magical effects. It's level 4 alchemy magic.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「It doesn't distinguish between friend and foe. Useful magic like party enhancement, illumination and levitation is no exception!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Wait a minute, Mr. Schwartz.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Hmm? What's wrong?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Anti-magic neutralizes all magic in the first place, right? Then wouldn't [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'] not work either?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You don't have to worry about that. There's an exception.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Anti-magic only affects a given area. If used from outside that space, even it can be removed.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「I see... So, if we use it...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Yes. It would counteract the anti-magic and allow you to use magic normally.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I understand...! Oh, but how can I obtain the [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'] spell...?」[k]
There are two types of magic: those that can be learned naturally by leveling up, and those that require a spellbook to learn.[k]
I know an Alchemist who can use level 9 alchemy magic, but didn't learn [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'].[k]
In other words, I can't just wait for members to level up and be able to use it. We need to get a spellbook or scroll somewhere.[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「I'm pretty sure I saw [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'] spellbooks at [b]Northrop Village Magic Shop[/b].」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Really?!」[k]
[b]Northrop Village[/b] is a snowy northern village at the end of the Yanek Forest, just past the caves. It's a bit far, but not inaccessible.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Understood! Thank you, Mr. Schwartz!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Mmm. Good luck, [テオ].」[k]
I may have seen a ray of hope. Someday, I'm sure I'll beat Blue![k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ここで今まで通り過ぎた場所の状態をまとめて更新する
[iscript]

// キャラの設定
game.lovers.push(o.ブルー);

o.テオ.equip.chest = void;
o.テオ.dressEquipment(o.布の服);
o.テオ.makeBustups();

o.リーゼル.strip.theo = "パンツ・幸せ";
o.リーゼル.strip.blue = "裸";
o.リーゼル.love.theo = 24;
o.リーゼル.love.blue = 12;
o.リーゼル.guard.blue = 0;
o.リーゼル.addSexRecordAndChangeHeart(%[date: game.date, guyKey: "ブルー", sexCount: 4
	, satisfy: 2, acts: ["正常位", "バック", "背面座位", "クリ責め"]]);
o.ブルー・ファミリア.addSlave(o.リーゼル);
o.リーゼル.removeEquipmentsByForce();
o.リーゼル.dressEquipment(o.ひものブラ,,, true);
o.リーゼル.dressEquipment(o.ひものパンツ,,, true);
o.リーゼル.events = [3];

o.マックス.exp += 20000;
o.マックス.levelUpToTheLast();
if(f.maxLastJob !== void) o.マックス.job = o[f.maxLastJob];
o.マックス.events = [6];

game.party.entry(o.マックス);
game.guest.entry(o.マリア);
game.party.recovery();

// クエスト
o.盗賊メンバー派遣の依頼.complete();
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.remove(o.盗賊メンバー派遣の依頼);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.remove(o.コボルド退治);
if(o.墓参り.completed) o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.remove(o.墓参り);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.add(o.ワイルド・ブルのアジトを探せ);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.add(o.スライム軍団の討伐);
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.quests.add(o.若さを維持したい);

o.かもめ亭.quests.remove(o.さらわれた少女たちの救出);
o.かもめ亭.quests.add(o.夫の捜索);
o.かもめ亭.quests.add(o.黄金のリンゴを届けてくれ);

o.マルティナの酒場.quests.remove(o.赤いネックレスを探してほしい);
o.マルティナの酒場.quests.remove(o.遺跡の財宝);
o.マルティナの酒場.quests.add(o.王の短剣);
o.マルティナの酒場.quests.add(o.黄金の人魚像を探してほしい);
o.マルティナの酒場.quests.add(o.妻の浮気調査);
o.マルティナの酒場.quests.add(o.兄に手紙を届けてくれ);

// 町
o.サファイアシティ・北西門.events = [];
o.サファイアシティ・北東門.events = [];
o.サファイアシティ・南西門.events = [];
o.サファイアシティ・南東門.events = [];
o.下水道入口.events = [];
o.王立ギルド.events = [];
o.待合所.events = [];
o.ベトリヌスの酒場.events = [25];
o.冒険者の宿.events = [];
o.マリオン武器工房.events = [];
o.鎧屋ドミンゴ.events = [];
o.世界一の道具店.events = [];
o.ドロシーの魔法店.events = [];
o.アウラ中央教会.events.assign(o.浜辺の教会.events);
o.イーラ中央寺院.events.assign(o.地下教会.events);
o.アイテム保管庫.events = [];
o.サファイア城.events = [];
o.闘技場.events.remove(9);
o.公園.events = [];
o.アイテム博物館.events = [];
o.マルティナの酒場.events = [7, 3];
o.ブルーのアジト.events = [0];
o.シーガルの村.events = [1];

o.自宅.appeared = false;
o.ブルーのアジト.appeared = true;
o.冒険者ギルド.appeared = true;
o.ホテル琥珀.appeared = true;
o.冒険者の保管庫.appeared = true;
o.ブレイブタウン・西門.appeared = true;

o.森の中の廃屋入口.requireMembers = true;
o.町外れの遺跡入口.requireMembers = true;

o.サファイアシティ.img = "town_sapphire";
game.townView.loadImages(o.サファイアシティ.img);

// マップ
o.コリンズの森.events.remove(10);
o.町外れの遺跡Ｂ１.events.push(5);
o.ブルーのアジト１Ｆ.events.push2(2, 4);

// ライバルチーム
o.ホーク・ウイング.boss = o.ルーファス;
o.ホーク・ウイング.gold = 366000;
o.ホーク・ウイング.itemsList = "";
o.ホーク・ウイング.members = [
