@gameon
@mu f=city
@w05
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...Okay, let's go!」[k]
The captivity period for the Blue Familia party led by Blue is [b][emb exp='o.ブルー・ファミリア.slaveTerm'] days[/b]. In other words, during that time, Riselle can't be taken back in any way.[k]
Until then, we should try to strengthen our party while looking for [emb exp='o.イレースマジック.displayName'], so that when the time comes, we can defeat Blue and take back Riselle.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Since Blue already found me, there's no point in sneaking around now. Maybe I should visit Bravetown, which I've been avoiding for a while.
 [k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
